Terraform is an infrastructure as code (IaC) tool that allows you to build, change, and version infrastructure safely and efficiently.
# Terraform document url: https://registry.terraform.io/providers/hashicorp/aws/latest/docs\
# Iaac ~> Infrastructure as a code 
# AWS Cloudformation => AWS
# Hasicorp terraform => all cloud platform
#TERRAFORM is written in hasicorp language

# ansible => configuration both on-prem/cloud
# terraform => infrastructure build tool

# code can be reused for later use =>code reuseability
# prereq => putty,puttygen,visual studio code

#INSTALLATION 
URL => https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/1.1.3/terraform_1.1.3_linux_amd64.zip
unzip terraform.zip
move the terraform execuitable file in /usr/local/bin/
terraform --version 
create a terraform file using .tf
terraform init
terraform plan 
terraform status 
terraform destroy








